<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Minimal Styling */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
            padding: 20px;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316 0%, #ea580c 100%);
            padding: 36px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .icon {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            font-size: 28px;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1e293b;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .intro-text {
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .otp-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff7ed 0%, #fffbeb 100%);
            border: 1px solid #fed7aa;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 32px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .otp-label {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #ea580c;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1.2px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 44px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dc2626;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', 'SF Mono', monospace;
            margin: 16px 0;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        
        .timer {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: #fef2f2;
            color: #dc2626;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 16px;
        }
        
        .instructions {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .instructions h3 {
            color: #0369a1;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .steps {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .steps li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            background: #0ea5e9;
            color: white;
            width: 22px;
            height: 22px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .security-alert {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 18px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .alert-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: #991b1b;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .alert-text {
            color: #991b1b;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            color: #64748b;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .contact {
            color: #3b82f6;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .contact:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content, .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .otp-code {
                font-size: 36px;
                letter-spacing: 6px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 22px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">üîê</div>
            <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</p>
            
            <p class="intro-text">
                We received a request to reset the password for your account. 
                Use the verification code below to reset your password.
            </p>
            
            <div class="otp-section">
                <div class="otp-label">Your Reset Code</div>
                <div class="otp-code"><%= otp %></div>
                <div class="timer">‚è∞ Valid for 15 minutes</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="instructions">
                <h3>üìù How to reset your password:</h3>
                <ul class="steps">
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-number">1</span>
                        <span>Return to the password reset page</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-number">2</span>
                        <span>Enter the 6-digit code above</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <span class="step-number">3</span>
                        <span>Create your new password</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-alert">
                <div class="alert-header">
                    <span>‚ö†Ô∏è</span>
                    <span>Important Security Notice</span>
                </div>
                <p class="alert-text">
                    If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. 
                    Your account remains secure. For security reasons, never share this code with anyone.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 25px;">
                Didn't request this? No changes have been made to your account yet. 
                You can safely delete this email.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@yourapp.com" class="contact">Contact our support team</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 12px;">¬© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Qwikish Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8;">
                This is an automated security message.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>